message.body: Happy birthday, you wonderful person! I thank goodness you were born! Have a great day!!!!
Having a good day? Despite the rain?
Awwww thank you my sweet! You make me smile :)
I actually haven't even left my house yet hahah. Partially due to the rain.
Sorry I won't be able to go out tonight, but I will tomorrow!!! It's been a rough week at work and I'm just so exhausted. If I went out, I'd just be falling asleep. But tomorrow, I'm all yours.
Yea no that's totally fine! That's why I suggested doing something tomorrow night because I knew some of us worked today and tomorrow will probably be the better option ;)
Or do?
Hahah almost no idea!
I wanted to enjoy the weather this weekend...
Oh yay!!
When I thought it was going to be nice and warm out!
But nope, it's going to rain!
Haha. I know. It sucks! Damn the rain. First really nice weekend and it rains. Figures.
Sucks. And there's a stupid girl on the train wearing shorts. People see 60 degrees and they think shorts.
Hahahah is it actually 60 degrees out today?
Yeah. Right now it's 65. It's pretty nice out.
Really??? I want to be outside!
Ehh. It's kinda dark and dreary.
It'd be great if it were sunny.
For some reason, it feels cold inside my house. That's why I didn't think it was that nice outside.
It's gonna get chilly later on. And it was rainy so it probably was colder.
Ughhhhh. I wanted to go for a walk. Just wanted to enjoy the day, leisurely hahah.
Spring will be around next week!
During the week right?? If course! Has to be in the 60s during the week!
I believe it'll be in the high fifties! Let's do the zombie thing too!!
Yes!!! I was thinking how I wanted to do that! Was waiting on what dates would be good for everyone since Sam is working on the weekends too.
Yeah but the living social deal is sold out. Didn't realize there was a cap. I just looked it up.
If we do it, it'd be $28.
What??? Oh man, people like zombies that much huh? Hahah.
They love being locked in a room with them I guess.
What has our world come to...
Zombie lovers. I do love zombie dreams though. They're like my favorite. It's the strangest thing.
What???!
I imagine it'd be the opposite.
Noooo!!! Makes it so awesome. Adrenaline rush. I don't know. Hahaha
We should go sky diving! Put that adrenaline to work.
